{
  "stem": "16313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stay over there in Szczecin, some other Polish cities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Szczecin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a Polish border-- not borders, it's in the-- it's-- it's-- it's in the west-- I mean, in West Poland and border of Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So and this time they start--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this time start with small things, start with like a-- a border, you know, on the border start shooting and this, and this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They check and they check.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No there-- there was not official war, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the end of '38.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In '39, there was this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, as a Jew, you feel-- you feel you're discriminated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you can-- you can't advance in the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can advance maybe one-- one stripe or two stripes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they got officers in Polish Army because they was doctors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The doctors, they must give them a special, like a Captain or something, because he's a doctor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Doctors or some other specialist-- highly-specialized people, mostly from Galicia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because Galicia belonged before the war, the First World War, belonged to Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They got more privileges.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these people over there got more education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they got over there, in this-- in this unions, they got some officers what's-- Jews what's officers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not so high office, and officers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the army?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not special--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The training is a regular training, like a soldier go through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, it was running and shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And going and working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because for a Jew, they discriminate you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They want to-- sometime you hear you're-- you're [INAUDIBLE] or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's you know what I mean, a-- a-- a Jewish guy, a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're less like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "it's like an insult, like a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
